    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>What Happened in Thanh Phong</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Rachel Stoll calls for comprehensive investigation into what happened in village of Thanh Phong under Bob Kerrey's leadership (Apr 29 article)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A comprehensive investigation seems essential. Let us not shrug our collective shoulders and say such is war and that Kerrey is a good man. Hope for a better future lies in closely scrutinizing our past actions. Let us do so even when -- especially when -- it hurts.</p>
        <p>Rachel Stoll  Jamaica, Vt.</p>
      </block>
